descriptor.name: 24 Mantra Organic Low Gi Rice - Gluten Free, 2 Kg
descriptor.short_desc: 24 Mantra Organic Low Gi Rice - Gluten Free, 2 Kg
descriptor.long_desc: 24 Mantra organic rice is flavourful medium-grained rice. Unlike its long-grained relative, it is shorter and moist. It means that after cooking, medium-grained rice tends to hold more water. Having low gi, our organic rice is useful for those sports and fitness enthusiasts who lose a lot of energy and strength exercising. It is excellent when used to make South Indian food like idlis, biryani, and rice porridge.
